---
<!-- Etapas da Experiência (Bento Grid) -->
<section class="py-section-gap-mobile md:py-section-gap-desktop bg-track-asphalt relative overflow-hidden" id="etapas">
  <!-- Background imagery for timeline -->
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/2 h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none mix-blend-screen hidden lg:block" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLuvzsXOWMtJ5nKK5X52hYtPuMaBqyAKhkh4UDN3byPEClkTnmL68M-RCY-AlGfqxmhQ2gWf_CMkCs0C2ydzzVWTVT39Lc8vSmlOxdMOdsUflUAZ_Gz0Jnn4LMsHP_ZiP6U2snibvPHsHrouYZD18e_8HpgmyLJ6fpDULOYUVCrnGxsRj7KNmBC0ayiHq2I8wdP2FvEZlXnldN2RZz1SILZxsUw6rmc6Mx0Cn-LN4_vCjCNWGovq2cwfL8M=w2560'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; filter: grayscale(100%);"></div>
  <div class="px-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal-hidden reveal-visible">
      <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Cronograma Executivo</p>
      <h2 class="font-section-title text-section-title text-performance-white uppercase">A Arquitetura do Dia</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8" id="networking">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="timeline-card bg-pit-lane-navy/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary/30 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 reveal-hidden delay-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5),_0_0_20px_rgba(200,160,40,0.15)] cursor-default">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
          <span class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[48px] text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-none drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0.5)]">01</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">local_cafe</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card-content">
          <h3 class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[28px] text-performance-white uppercase mb-2 tracking-wider group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Executive Briefing</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-microcopy text-metallic-grey leading-relaxed">Welcome coffee reservado. Credenciamento nominal, entrega de kits e primeiro contato com o grupo selecionado em ambiente formatado para networking orgânico.</p>
          <div class="timeline-card-extra">
            <p class="font-microcopy text-primary/80 mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">Dress code: Smart Casual Sport</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="timeline-card bg-pit-lane-navy/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary/30 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 reveal-hidden delay-200 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5),_0_0_20px_rgba(200,160,40,0.15)] cursor-default">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
          <span class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[48px] text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-none drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0.5)]">02</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">model_training</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card-content">
          <h3 class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[28px] text-performance-white uppercase mb-2 tracking-wider group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Track Academy & Safety</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-microcopy text-metallic-grey leading-relaxed">Instrução técnica com pilotos profissionais em sala climatizada. Análise de traçado, pontos de frenagem, dinâmica veicular e protocolos estritos de segurança na pista.</p>
          <div class="timeline-card-extra">
            <p class="font-microcopy text-primary/80 mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">Foco: Telemetria Básica & Seg.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="timeline-card bg-pit-lane-navy/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary/30 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 relative reveal-hidden delay-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5),_0_0_20px_rgba(200,160,40,0.15)] cursor-default overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Subtle image background for the main event card -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500 z-0 mix-blend-screen" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLuJVpvtrmp6VVIsWEazFlZ5Z5wFAO9mrBQQT8fBDQXnNXcrtk-Gh5frYytetl5UBSyoC3m9Dj1rAnkkpfZaFJlVbFny651yQtgSLtyvB1e-tWzUNz5_haAonxlcmVXtFQa_xrSpG7fm52j26-3gulskg-wH9wUTXwi5bT9ibTTuYoJt39xPQIZvf8MZvs2BluN_vU_NmVseaz7IYFDYNlqnskz1GBud53FP-Fo78ER8Go6FQ5VoQZQo0hY=w2560'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6 relative z-10">
          <span class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[48px] text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-none drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0.5)]">03</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">speed</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card-content relative z-10">
          <h3 class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[28px] text-performance-white uppercase mb-2 tracking-wider group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Open Track Sessions</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-microcopy text-metallic-grey leading-relaxed">Baterias exclusivas na pista. Tráfego rigorosamente controlado para garantir segurança e espaço para extrair o máximo do equipamento.</p>
          <div class="timeline-card-extra">
            <p class="font-microcopy text-primary/80 mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">Formato: Baterias de 30min</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="timeline-card bg-pit-lane-navy/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary/30 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 reveal-hidden delay-400 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5),_0_0_20px_rgba(200,160,40,0.15)] cursor-default">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
          <span class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[48px] text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-none drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0.5)]">04</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">handshake</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card-content">
          <h3 class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[28px] text-performance-white uppercase mb-2 tracking-wider group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Pit Lane Business</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-microcopy text-metallic-grey leading-relaxed">Lounge vip nos boxes operando em paralelo. Open bar (não alcoólico), alta gastronomia e ambiente propício para discussões de negócios de alto nível.</p>
          <div class="timeline-card-extra">
            <p class="font-microcopy text-primary/80 mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">Acesso contínuo durante pista</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 5 -->
      <div class="timeline-card bg-pit-lane-navy/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary/30 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 reveal-hidden delay-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5),_0_0_20px_rgba(200,160,40,0.15)] cursor-default">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
          <span class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[48px] text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors leading-none drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0)] group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(237,193,72,0.5)]">05</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">sports_bar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card-content">
          <h3 class="font-hero-headline-mobile text-[28px] text-performance-white uppercase mb-2 tracking-wider group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Sunset Cigar & Drink</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-microcopy text-metallic-grey leading-relaxed">Encerramento da pista seguido por happy hour premium. Degustação de charutos e consolidação das conexões feitas ao longo do dia.</p>
          <div class="timeline-card-extra">
            <p class="font-microcopy text-primary/80 mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]">Experiência: Premium Spirits</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 6 (Visual Grid Balancer) -->
      <div class="timeline-card bg-pit-lane-navy/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-2 border-primary/30 aspect-square md:aspect-auto min-h-[300px] relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-primary hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 reveal-hidden delay-600 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5),_0_0_20px_rgba(200,160,40,0.15)]">
        <img 
          alt="Luxury Racing Detail" 
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-luminosity opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700" 
          src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLuJVpvtrmp6VVIsWEazFlZ5Z5wFAO9mrBQQT8fBDQXnNXcrtk-Gh5frYytetl5UBSyoC3m9Dj1rAnkkpfZaFJlVbFny651yQtgSLtyvB1e-tWzUNz5_haAonxlcmVXtFQa_xrSpG7fm52j26-3gulskg-wH9wUTXwi5bT9ibTTuYoJt39xPQIZvf8MZvs2BluN_vU_NmVseaz7IYFDYNlqnskz1GBud53FP-Fo78ER8Go6FQ5VoQZQo0hY=w2560"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-pit-lane-navy via-transparent to-transparent opacity-80"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 z-10">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[32px] animate-breathe">workspace_premium</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
